---
source: tests/error_envelope_golden.rs
assertion: all DomainError variants produce ee.error.v1 compliant JSON envelopes
schema:
  error: ee.error.v1
contracts:
  - error envelope includes schema field set to "ee.error.v1"
  - error.code is lowercase_snake_case matching the DomainError variant
  - error.message contains human-readable description
  - error.severity is "low", "medium", or "high" per documented exit codes
  - error.repair is optional but present when actionable fix is available
  - error.details is always present (empty object {} for most variants)
  - NotFound variant includes resource and id in details
severity_mapping:
  low:
    - usage (exit code 1)
    - not_found (exit code 1)
  medium:
    - configuration (exit code 2)
    - search_index (exit code 4)
    - graph (exit code 4)
    - import (exit code 5)
    - unsatisfied_degraded_mode (exit code 6)
    - policy_denied (exit code 7)
    - migration_required (exit code 8)
  high:
    - storage (exit code 3)
    - migration_drift (exit code 8)
evidence:
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_usage_with_repair.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_usage_without_repair.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_configuration.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_storage.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_search_index.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_graph.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_import.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_not_found.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_unsatisfied_degraded_mode.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_policy_denied.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_migration_required.snap
  - tests/snapshots/error_envelope_golden__error_envelope_migration_drift.snap
